{
  "texts": [
    "Why should I go to them again?\"",
    "4 The Lord replied, \"You are concerned for the plant that shaded you, though it was here today and gone tomorrow.",
    "Should I not also be concerned for the people of Nineveh, who cannot tell their left from their right?",
    "Go once more and speak my words, that they may continue to turn from evil and walk the path of righteousness.\"",
    "5 So Jonah set out for the great city of Nineveh, as the Lord commanded."
  ]
}